{"word":"G948 - βδελύσσω - bdelýssō - bdel-oos'-so - Abhor","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">βδελύσσω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">bdelýssō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">bdel-oos'-so</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Abhor</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அருவரு"},{"paragraph":"to render foul, to cause to be abhorred"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a (presumed) derivative of<b>&#x03B2;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9;</b> <b>bdeo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>stink</i>); to <i>be disgusted</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>detest</i> (especially of idolatry): - abhor, abominable.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G946/946\">G946</a>, <a href=\"#/G947/947\">G947</a>, <a href=\"#/G948/948\">G948</a>"}]}